                            <note> This manuscript contains commentary on the book of Aphorisms
                                attributed to <persName type="standard"
                                  ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/287984736"
                                  key="n 80119944 ">Hippocrates</persName>. This is a lemmatically arranged
                                commentary. The first several folios are missing, so the beginning
                                of the copy is a middle of comm. on i. 5. The beginning of each of
                                Bk2-7 is as follow: Bk 2: f. 24a; Bk 3: f. 57a; Bk 4: f. 80a; Bk 5:
                                f. 123b; Bk 6: f. 151a; Bk 7: f. 201b. Folios <locus>63</locus> and
                                    <locus>66</locus> are missing.</note>
